text: Kruchinino () is a rural locality (a village) in Nikolayevsky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 10 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 32 km from Ufa, 6 km from Nikolayevka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ufimsky District
title: Kruchinino
